lead_paragraph: The Golden State Warriors did not skip a beat without key point guard Stephen Curry, routing the Houston Rockets 114-81 on Wednesday to seal a 4-1 series triumph in the first round of the Western Conference playoffs.

headline.print_headline: No Curry, No Worry as Warriors Eliminate Rockets
